    • search

      public String search​(String text, String key, String algorithm)
      This method will find the word or letter by the algorithm that is selected by the user.
      Parameters:
      text - is a variable type String that put all the text that have the "txt". text != null
      key - is a variable type String and is the word or letter that user want to find. key != null
      algorithm - is a variable type String that is the algorithm selected by the user. algorithm != "Select algorithm"
      Returns:
      pos that is a variable type String with the text find
